Show HN: OneTimeData – Data that you may need once in your lifetime
text: Sometimes you need data to insert into your database or do analytics. You should search and find this data and convert it to your desired format. This project aims to collect these data and prepare common formats, e.g., CSV, JSON, and SQL.
